Feature: Stock service in catalog

  A Customer can reserve a Activity by providing his credit card details

  Scenario: Reserve a Activity
    Given a customer named "John" with the credit card number "1234567890"
    And a Activity named "Trekking" with the description "Trekking in the montains" and the price 100 without advantages
    When he adds the Activity "Trekking" for the date "07-11 21:30" to his cart
    And he proceeds to checkout
    Then a transaction of 100 should appear on the Transaction History of "John"
    And the Activity "Trekking" should be reserved

